        <trans-unit id="107" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The code then calls the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawImage%2A&gt;</ph> method of a <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Drawing.Graphics&gt;</ph> object to draw a portion of the apple image in a destination rectangle that is larger than the original apple image.</source>
